      <title>韩国任命经济学家为应对生育危机的助手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-korea-names-economist-as-aide-to-tackle-fertility-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈任命一名经济学家担任新任高级秘书，以提高韩国的出生率。韩国的出生率位居世界最低，对长期经济前景构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-korea-names-economist-as-aide-to-tackle-fertility-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:14:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政策不连贯导致南非气候目标落空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-africa-s-climate-ambitions-derailed-by-incoherent-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统任命的一个咨询机构表示，南非未能实现其应对和准备气候变化的雄心勃勃的目标和承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/south-africa-s-climate-ambitions-derailed-by-incoherent-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
